com.vector.cfg.automation.scripting.api

Interface IScriptTaskUserDefinedArgument<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the value type of the argument.

    @PublishedApi(value=ADDITIONS_ALLOWED)
 @PublishedApiDomain(value=AUTOMATION_IF)
public interface IScriptTaskUserDefinedArgument<T>
    IScriptTaskUserDefinedArgument defines an script user defined argument create during IScriptTask by an IScriptCreationApi.IScriptTaskBuilder. The actual value of the argument could be retrieve during IScriptTask execution, by calling getValue() or getValues().

    (c) Copyright Vctr Informatik GmbH. All Rights Reserved.

    See Also:
    IScriptCreationApi, IScriptCreationApi.IScriptTaskBuilder, IScriptTask
